枚举 Option

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Option>

    public enum Option
extends java.lang.Enum<Option>
    Options for javac. The specific Option to handle a command-line option is identified by searching the members of this enum in order, looking the first match. The action for an Option is performed by calling process, and by providing a suitable OptionHelper to provide access the compiler state.

    This is NOT part of any supported API. If you write code that depends on this, you do so at your own risk. This code and its internal interfaces are subject to change or deletion without notice.
